data.description: Privacy and scenic views await you in this tucked away home. Main floor formal dining area leads to the deck where you can sip coffee overlooking the peaceful Sheboygan River and Kiwanis park.  Quiet wooded lot allows additional privacy.  HW floors throughout main and upper rooms..  First floor laundry for convenience. Upper large  primary bedroom with private bath brings natural light and comfort.  Additional spacious upper bedroom with built in bookcase has so many possibilities.   Lower level has separate rear entrance and offers a 2nd full kitchen and entertaining area with bonus room.  Do not wait to make this tranquil home yours.
